Company Overview of HSBC Bank Bermuda Limited



Snapshot¬†People




Company Overview
HSBC Bank Bermuda Limited provides financial services to individuals, institutions, and corporations in Bermuda and internationally. The company‚Äôs deposit products include chequing and savings accounts, and fixed term deposits. It also provides education, green, personal, and home loans; overdrafts; personal lines of credit; residential mortgages; and credit and debit cards. In addition, the company offers various financial planning and investment products; and home buildings, home contents, mortgage protection, motor, consumer loan protection, travel, and marine insurance products. Further, it provides working capital and growth finance, payment and collection, risk management, foreign exch...
HSBC Bank Bermuda Limited provides financial services to individuals, institutions, and corporations in Bermuda and internationally. The company‚Äôs deposit products include chequing and savings accounts, and fixed term deposits. It also provides education, green, personal, and home loans; overdrafts; personal lines of credit; residential mortgages; and credit and debit cards. In addition, the company offers various financial planning and investment products; and home buildings, home contents, mortgage protection, motor, consumer loan protection, travel, and marine insurance products. Further, it provides working capital and growth finance, payment and collection, risk management, foreign exchange, and Internet banking services. Additionally, the company offers investment management, and custodial and other fiduciary services, as well as fund and trust administration services. The company was founded in 1889 and is headquartered in Hamilton, Bermuda. HSBC Bank Bermuda Limited is a subsidiary of HSBC Asia Holdings BV.
Detailed Description


