HSBC Bank Bermuda Limited Key Developments

HSBC Bank Bermuda Limited Announces Consolidated Earnings Results for the Year Ended Dec. 31, 2015
Mar 4 16
HSBC Bank Bermuda Limited announced consolidated earnings results for the year ended Dec. 31, 2015. Net profit was $87 million, an increase of $39 million or 81% compared with $48 million in the prior year. Net operating income was $268 million, an increase of $7 million or 3%.


HSBC Bank Bermuda Limited Names Mr. Mark Watkinson as Chief Executive Officer
Sep 1 15
HSBC Bank Malta p.l.c. announced that Mr. Mark Watkinson will be appointed as chief executive officer of HSBC Bank Bermuda Limited, subject to regulatory approval in Bermuda. Mr. Mark Watkinson presently working as chief executive officer of HSBC Bank Malta p.l.c.


